Lesser Magic Missile
Evocation Cantrip
Casting Time: 1 action
Range: 60 feet
Target: A creature of your choice that you can see within range
Components: V, S
Duration: Instantaneous
You create a small glowing dart of magical force. It hits the target dealing 1 point of force damage.

This spellâ€™s damage increases by 1 when you reach 5th level (2), 11th level (3), and 17th (4).



Overmaster
2nd level Abjuration
Casting Time: 1 Action
Range: Self
Target: Self
Components: V, S
Duration: 1 minute
The next time you cast a spell before this spell ends, that spell cannot be interrupted by counterspell, or cancelled or absorbed by any similar effects. This spell then ends.

This does not prevent the next spell you cast being suppressed by an antimagic field.
